    <a href="" class="js-vertical-tab-accordion-heading vertical-tab-accordion-heading" rel="tab2">How It Works</a>
    <div id="tab2" class="js-vertical-tab-content vertical-tab-content steps">
    <h4 clas='tab-headers'>How It Works:</h4>
      <ol>
      <li>First you <a href="/users/new">create an account</a> with us, using your first name, last name and email address</li>
      <li>Using our secure bank login provided by PLAID and your financial institution, you authorize us to round up each of your transactions from an account of your choosing</li>
      <li>Utilizing our search&mdash;powered by <a href="http://orghunter.com/">OrgHunter</a>&mdash;you choose from over 2 million charities in the United States</li>
      <li>Throughout the month, we round up the transactions you make and ear-mark that amount for the charity that you've chosen</li>
      <li>At the end of the month, we debit that amount from your securely authorized account and, in partnership with <a href="http://makemydonation.org/">MakeMyDonation</a>, we send the donation amount to your charity</li>
      <li>On the first of the month, your 'round-ups' reset and you start earning donations all over again!</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

